stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> requested
    requested --> identity_verified: identity checks pass
    identity_verified --> conformance_passed: schema + signature + profile pass
    conformance_passed --> probation: governance admission
    probation --> active: reliability threshold met
    active --> restricted: policy violation or risk event
    restricted --> active: remediation accepted
    restricted --> revoked: severe or repeated failure
    revoked --> [*]

    classDef early fill:#1e293b,stroke:#64748b,color:#94a3b8
    classDef mid fill:#172554,stroke:#818cf8,color:#c4b5fd
    classDef good fill:#052e16,stroke:#4ade80,color:#bbf7d0
    classDef warn fill:#451a03,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#fde68a
    classDef bad fill:#450a0a,stroke:#f87171,color:#fecaca

    class requested early
    class identity_verified early
    class conformance_passed mid
    class probation mid
    class active good
    class restricted warn
    class revoked bad
